data.description: Welcome to your future home in the heart of Duluth, Georgia! This cozy 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom  property is now available for sale, offering an excellent opportunity for homeowners and  investors alike.  This property is being sold in "As Is" condition, providing you with the chance to customize and  update it according to your preferences and needs. Whether you're looking to invest, renovate, or  make it your forever home, this property has incredible potential.  Foundation: Cement Accepted offers will close with the seller's title company, ensuring a smooth and efficient  transaction process. Act fast, as opportunities like this one don't come around often!
